Last access time in seconds since the epoch
.IP "blksize" 4
.IX Item "blksize"
Preferred block size for file system I/O
.IP "blocks" 4
.IX Item "blocks"
Actual number of blocks allocated
.IP "ctime" 4
.IX Item "ctime"
Inode change time in seconds since the epoch
.IP "device" 4
